body:
We Are Looking for:

Experienced software developer with relevant knowledge of C/C++ for our office in Cluj-Napoca.


The Project:

Our customer provides software solutions to plan, simulate, view in 3D and improve factory production activities, both automated and which require a human worker.

We are working together with the customer’s team in developing and maintaining those products.


Responsibilities:

Development of client requirements, including analyzing the requirements and discussing the technical solution with our client.


Required Competencies:

Mandatory:
• C++ experience
• basic Qt programming experience

Nice to have:
• Experience with CMake and QML
• Computer Graphics know-how
• COM know-how
• AutoCAD know-how (user and/or ObjectArx, ActiveX api)


We Value:

• Respect
• Reliability
• Strive for Excellence 





			    $(document).ready(function() { 
			    var allVideos = $('.job-video-container object, .job-video-container embed, .job-video-container iframe'); 
			    var oldWidth = allVideos.width();
			    var oldHeight =  allVideos.height();
			    var aspectRatioOS = oldHeight/oldWidth; 
			    allVideos.removeAttr('height').removeAttr('width');
			    function resizeVideoOSJS(){
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%;');
				var widthInit = allVideos.width();
				var heightInit = widthInit * aspectRatioOS;
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%; min-height: 220px; height: '+ heightInit +'px;');
				//.attr('width',  widthInit).attr('height', allVideos.height())    
			    }
			    resizeVideoOSJS();
				    window.onresize = resizeVideoOSJS; 
			    });
